{"tid":495763,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人同父母關係好差？","createTime":"2017-12-11T04:08:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-11T19:20:28.000Z","uid":45055,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"82bd3a8d4830639cf14e1bf84330494dacdd10fb","tid":495763,"uid":45055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T04:08:50.000Z","msg":"唔係講話老豆老母成日管住好煩個種<br />\n而係好似一齊住既陌生人咁<br />\n<br />\n平時同老豆好少講野<br />\n老母就自從知佢係出面flirt d 後生仔之後就冇同佢講過野<br />\n到我生日佢地又唔會記得<br />\n食飯都係各自返房食<br />\n由中學開始揀科讀咩U咩major全部都係自己決定<br />\n通常係決定完之後過左一兩年佢先知原來我讀緊個樣野<br />\n<br />\n但係物質上某程度係我想要咩就有咩<br />\n所以都幾感激佢地<br />\n出黎做野一定會比返咁多佢地洗<br />\n<br />\n但係所有既人生大事我都唔會想同佢同分享<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最好就之後畢業結婚生仔佢地都唔會參與<br />\n<br />\n我本身以為正常人同父母都唔會話太close<br />\n係尾同人傾計先知原來我屋企既呢種關係係佢地眼中係好奇怪<br />\n<br />\n有冇人都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39c6c3fab6c031c0d3b1ada2a4c48fa1b98a21e6","tid":495763,"uid":162406,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T04:13:06.000Z","msg":"表示自己係出面係個highper仔<br />\n返到屋企唔講野 好驚比人煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc9d6e21ae68baa0cfb41a1da5095aaf5a1a19b9","tid":495763,"uid":57835,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T06:21:08.000Z","msg":"成日鬧鳩我好似得罪左佢咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a18e6102d665fe44fb65d293c26dbe15aad4885","tid":495763,"uid":57835,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T06:22:11.000Z","msg":"反擊佢又無曬面，我都費事理<br />\n我好撚忙架嘛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f49c74fe4e41b74c42134b81cc134e9c2de214c6","tid":495763,"uid":55309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T06:23:02.000Z","msg":"揮手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b43c201de0634d4168680bf39c53ca17e697feeb","tid":495763,"uid":3028,"like":1,